def get_tiles(name):
    url = "https://geoserveis.icgc.cat/servei/catalunya/mapa-base/wmts/{0}/".format(name) + "MON3857NW/{z}/{x}/{y}.png"
    attributions = dict(
        vector=(
            'Catalunya: <a href="https://www.icgc.cat/"> ICGC</a> '
            '(<a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">CC BY 4.0</a>)'
            ' |\nWorld:  OpenMapTiles '
            ' <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright">OpenStreetMap contributors</a>'
        ),
        image=(
            'Catalunya: <a href="https://www.icgc.cat/"> ICGC</a> '
            '(<a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">CC BY 4.0</a>)'
            ' |\nWorld: Esri, DigitalGlobe, USDA, USGS, GeoEye, Getmapping,\nAeroGRID, IGN, IGP, UPR-EGP, and the GIS community  Esri'
        )
    )
    if name in ['topografic', 'topografic-gris', 'estandard', 'simplificat', 'administratiu']:
        attribution = attributions['vector']
    elif name in ['orto', 'orto-gris', 'orto-hibrida']:
        attribution = attributions['image']
    else:
        attribution = ""
    return maptiles_zxy(url=url, attribution=attribution)

def get_plot(name):
    return ggplot() + \
        geom_livemap(tiles=get_tiles(name)) + \
        ggtitle("ICGC_{0}".format(name.replace("-", "_").upper()))
In[4]:
gggrid([
    get_plot('topografic'),
    get_plot('topografic-gris'),
    get_plot('estandard'),
    get_plot('simplificat'),
    get_plot('administratiu'),
    get_plot('orto'),
    get_plot('orto-gris'),
    get_plot('orto-hibrida'),
], ncol=2)
